data.title: SQUARE ENIX
data.meta_description: FOAMSTARS, the fresh new 4v4 online party shooter for PlayStation from Square Enix!
data.text:
AboutAbout

Introducing FOAMSTARS, the new 4v4 online party shooter for PlayStation5 and PlayStation4.

Use foam to build terrain, creating slippery surfaces to surf around the arena at high speed, help defend from enemy attacks, or create vantage points to take out opponents.

And most importantly, to foam up the opposition!
